QuestData.Title: Operation: Relocation
QuestData.Description:
Devourers have disrupted the avians nesting at Provis Esper.
This may be our last chance to examine them before they become tainted, like the others.
Capture several of the avians at Provis Esper and return them to Pilgrim Arizh for relocation and study. Deal with any problems that get in your way.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver $2oa wrangled Wild Proto Avians and slay $3oa Soul-Parched Gorgers and $4oa Reality Breachers in Provis Esper.
QuestData.RewardText: Well done, $n. The avians will be moved to a safer location where we can observe them.
